kibana
| selectFilter
| esdocs index="search-movies" fields="directors, awards.wins"

  labelFont={font align="center" color="#ec77a8" family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" italic=false size=14 underline=false weight="normal"} metricFormat="0,0.[000]"
| render

kibana
| selectFilter
| demodata
| pointseries x="time" y="mean(price)"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle lines=1 fill=1}
| render

shape "speechBubble" fill="#4cbce4" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render
